         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">23/12/86 ¶  ¶ It seems best to me, esteemed Mr Tepper, that the description of your pretty  ¶ Candollea ¶  should still be published  ¶ in this year ¶ , so that no one else otherwise describes the spe...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">86.12.23</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Otto Tepper</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">RB MSS M198, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>MS annotation by Tepper: 'Reply to date 30.12.86'.</p>
               </note>23/12/86</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Mir schien es am Besten, geehrter Herr Tepper, dass die Beschreibung Ihrer niedlichen <name key="Candollea">Candollea</name> noch in </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">diesem Jahre</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style=""> erscheinen sollte, damit nicht etwa noch sonst Jemand die Art im selben Jahre beschriebe. Selbstverständlich kann ja die Beschreibung in den Veröffentlichungen der dortigen R.S wiederholt werden, mit nachträglichen Notizen von Ihnen.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ich werde Alph de Candolle, der sich den Achtziger nähert, aber von dem ich eben wieder einen wohlgemuthen Brief habe, so wie von dem noch älteren Owen, die Käng. Insel <name key="Candollea">Candollea</name> in einem Ex senden. Ich bin recht </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">bedrängt</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style=""> im Departement, da ich gewissermassen gezwungen bin, den "Key" </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">bald</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style=""> zu vollenden. Wenn ich also einige Ihrer Pflanzen nicht gleich zum Abschluss bringe, so wissen Sie den Grund. Etwas </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">sehr Merk</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style="">würdiges, wie die <name key="Candollea">Candollea</name>, werde ich aber immer gleich vornehmen.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ihre Glückwünsche zum Fest u Jahreswechsel aufs Innigste erwiedernd Ihr</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">23/12/86</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>It seems best to me, esteemed Mr Tepper, that the description of your pretty <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <name key="Candollea">Candollea</name>
               </seg> should still be published <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">in this year</hi>
               </seg>, so that no one else otherwise describes the species in the same year.<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>M published <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                        <name key="Candollea">Candollea</name> tepperiana</seg> in B87.01.01, issued on 1 January 1887.</p>
               </note> Of course the description can indeed be repeated in the publications of the R. S. there,<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Royal Society of SA.</p>
               </note> with additional notes from you.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I will send a specimen of the Kang. Island<note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Kangaroo Island, SA.</p>
               </note>
               <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <name key="Candollea">Candollea</name>
               </seg> to Alph. de Candolle, who is approaching his eighties, but from whom I just have a cheerful letter again, as well as from the even older Owen.<note xml:id="ftn5" type="footnote" n="5">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Letters not found.</p>
               </note> I am very <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">pressed</hi>
               </seg> in the department, since to some extent I am forced to complete the "Key" <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">soon</hi>
               </seg>.<note xml:id="ftn6" type="footnote" n="6">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>B88.13.03.</p>
               </note> Therefore if I do not finish some of your plants immediately, you know the reason. However, anything <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">very</hi>
               </seg> noteworthy, such as the <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <name key="Candollea">Candollea</name>
               </seg>, I will always immediately attend to.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Most cordially reciprocating your felicitations for the festival and turn of the year your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Candollea">Candollea</name>
            </p>
         </div>
